 * Lamon APP is an economic investment game built on a decentralized smart contract by Binance Smart Chain.
 *
 * You create your plantations with Lamons and make a profit.
 *
 * Accruals profit every second
 *
 * Works only with USDT BSC-BEP20
 *
 * Web: https://lamon.app/
 *
